metadata.name: Residence 001
metadata.description:
Diffused Mid-Century is my earliest architecture work. This series developed in November 2021 and created with JAX Diffusion was the beginning of my obsession with architecture and design-based projects. These pieces were abstract experiments in seasons, locations, and blending into their surroundings. 

Six of these works were minted originally the Solana Blockchain. Their Solsea page still active for provenance. Buying has been disabled on the original Solana pieces.

https://solsea.io/c/618d97446e28952ab8b173b4
